title: BRIEF-Ekinops deploys 100G compatible monofiber solution for Céliéno net
text:
BRIEF-Ekinops deploys 100G compatible monofiber solution for Céliéno net 
Oct 19 Ekinops SA : 
* Says to have deployed a mono scalable fiber solution to 100g (100 gigabit/second) for the Céliéno Paris-Chartres optic network
